  <brief_title>AISTCM-Outcome Measurement of Acute Ischemic Stroke With Traditional Chinese Medicine</brief_title>
  <official_title>AISTCM-The Pathological Pattern Differentiation and Outcome Measurement of Acute Ischemic Stroke Treated With Traditional Chinese Medicine</official_title>
  <sponsors>
